# Built application files *.apk *.ap_ *.aab
# Files for the ART/Dalvik VM *.dex
# Java class files *.class
# Generated files bin/ gen/ out/ release/
# Gradle files .gradle/ build/
# Local configuration file (sdk path, etc) local.properties
# Proguard folder generated by Eclipse proguard/
# Log Files *.log
# Android Studio Navigation editor temp files .navigation/
# Android Studio captures folder captures/
# IntelliJ *.iml .idea/workspace.xml .idea/tasks.xml .idea/gradle.xml .idea/assetWizardSettings.xml .idea/dictionaries .idea/libraries .idea/caches .idea/modules.xml .idea/.name .idea/compiler.xml .idea/misc.xml .idea/deploymentTargetSelector.xml .idea/inspectionProfiles/ .idea/artifacts .idea/kotlinc.xml .idea/vcs.xml
# Keystore files *.jks *.keystore
# External native build folder generated in Android Studio 2.2 and later .externalNativeBuild .cxx/
# Google Services (contains API KEYS and secrets) # Uncomment if you want to exclude it from git # app/google-services.json
# Version control vcs.xml
# lint lint/intermediates/ lint/generated/ lint/outputs/ lint/tmp/ lint-results.xml lint-results_files/
# Android Profiling *.hprof
# OS-specific files .DS_Store .DS_Store? ._* .Spotlight-V100 .Trashes ehthumbs.db Thumbs.db
# KSP Generated files app/build/generated/
# Kotlin *.kotlin_module
